Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,新浪微博 @摆渡字幕组 发布\N关注微博 掌握最新字幕资源
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,翻译：Emma Watson/key/呵呵/Margaret
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,翻译：enchanted/张天烊/不酸的柠檬/初夏晚夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,校对：JayJayLiu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,摆渡字幕组翻译/APP开发志愿者招募中 报名群:377256405
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,“但你如果作恶 就该惧怕\N{\fs25}"But if you do wrong, be afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他佩带刀剑就是为了惩恶扬善\N{\fs25}{\fs25}for he does not bear the sword in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他是神的仆役\N{\fs25}He is the servant of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是降临震怒到作恶人身上\N{\fs25}an avenger who carries out God's wrath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,的报应者“\N{\fs25}on the wrongful."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,每当我读到圣经《罗马书》13:4时\N{\fs25}I often thought of my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我总会想起我的朋友\N{\fs25}Officer Reginald Dean Davis,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,雷金纳德 · 迪安 · 戴维斯警官\N{\fs25}when I would read Romans 13:4.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在他被残忍杀害之前\N{\fs25}That he punished two of the three men who attacked him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他惩罚了袭击他的三个人中的两个\N{\fs25}before he himself was killed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.35,0:01:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,正因如此 每当我吟诵这一段圣经时\N{\fs25}means I will never think of anyone else ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这经文只属于他一个人\N{\fs25}when I read or speak this verse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他为保护家人而死\N{\fs25}He died protecting his family,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为保护朋友 保护这座城市而牺牲\N{\fs25}his friends and this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾是神的仆役\N{\fs25}He was a servant of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我常通过一些事来安慰自己\N{\fs25}I assuage my rage that a third man escaped
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,以缓解我对逃脱的第三者的愤怒\N{\fs25}by trying to remind myself of a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,首先\N{\fs25}First,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,雷金纳德找到了一位\N{\fs25}Reginald found a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,和她一样坚强 进取 机敏的妻子\N{\fs25}as strong, driven and smart as he.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,其次 是他的儿子\N{\fs25}And then I think of his boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈\N{\fs25}Andre,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,从他身上我看到了和他父亲一样的品质\N{\fs25}and I see the same, sometimes infuriating,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,无畏无惧\N{\fs25}fearlessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,求知若渴\N{\fs25}inquisitiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你现在不这么想\N{\fs25}I know it may not feel like it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但 安德烈 这十三年你从你父亲身上学到的\N{\fs25}but you got more from your father, Andre, in 13 years
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,比大多数男人穷尽一生学到的都多\N{\fs25}than most men will in a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他教会你遵循自己良知\N{\fs25}He taught you to follow your conscience,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不以人云亦云来判断对错\N{\fs25}to not take anyone else's word about what is right and wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个残酷的世界里\N{\fs25}to find a just code
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻到公平与正义\N{\fs25}in an often cruel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,十九年后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你在下班时抽出时间来内务局\N{\fs25}Thank you for making time for IA at the end of your shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我别无选择\N{\fs25}I didn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以选择不当警察\N{\fs25}You could choose not to be a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,当警察这件事不是我能决定的\N{\fs25}Being a cop isn't a choice for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么决定的？\N{\fs25}What is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,基因\N{\fs25}DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今 我觉得我们没必要解释\N{\fs25}At this point, we don't need to spell out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我们都在这儿\N{\fs25}why we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不 得解释 这是官方程序\N{\fs25}Yes, we do. Official procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,任何警官在执行任务使用武器时\N{\fs25}Any officer who discharges his or her weapon in the line of duty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,都必须证明每一次开火都是恰当合理的\N{\fs25}must justify every round of ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你九年杀了八个人\N{\fs25}You've shot eight people in nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是 枪法精准 一人不留\N{\fs25}Good shootings. Cleared on all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你当上警探以来杀了三个\N{\fs25}Three since you were made detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有四个了\N{\fs25}Four now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那个幸存的被判处终身监禁不得释放\N{\fs25}The one who survived was sentenced to life without.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你有对任何一个后悔过吗\N{\fs25}Do you regret any?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过心理医生了\N{\fs25}I've been to the psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有回答我的问题\N{\fs25}That's not an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我一点也不后悔\N{\fs25}No, I do not regret any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你睡觉时不会梦见他们的脸吗？\N{\fs25}Faces don't come to you in your sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,正义是需要代价的\N{\fs25}Justice comes at a cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,正义与否不是由你来裁决的\N{\fs25}Justice is not determined by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但我就在那裁决的最前线\N{\fs25}But I am the sharp end of that determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谁告诉你的？\N{\fs25}Says who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我的警徽\N{\fs25}My badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我入职时的宣誓\N{\fs25}My oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你的基因？\N{\fs25}Your DNA?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,南北战争的时候\N{\fs25}During the Civil War,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一些士兵只是在不停给步枪上膛 却未曾开过火\N{\fs25}some soldiers just kept loading their muskets without ever firing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一次装了五六发枪弹\N{\fs25}Five or six balls loaded on top of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,越南战争时 只有百分之三十的前线步兵开过枪\N{\fs25}In Vietnam, only 30% of frontline infantry soldiers ever fired a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说 打仗时十个士兵里只有三个真正在战斗\N{\fs25}So, ten soldiers in battle, only three truly fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的想要用战争来类比吗 警探戴维斯？\N{\fs25}Are you really using war analogies here, Detective Davis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为另外七个在干什么？\N{\fs25}What do you imagine the other seven were doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 安德烈你来了\N{\fs25}Hi, Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她情况如何？\N{\fs25}How's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很疲劳 不过我给她喂过药了\N{\fs25}Tired, but I just gave her her meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 你可以回家了 这里交给我吧\N{\fs25}All right, you can head home. I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要我 你知道怎么找我\N{\fs25}You know where to find me if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在看什么呢？\N{\fs25}What are we watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你丢下了我\N{\fs25}You left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 妈妈 我有一堆忙事儿\N{\fs25}No, Ma. I had to pull a triple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里呆太久了\N{\fs25}I've been here too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我……\N{\fs25}I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是在这儿呆太久了\N{\fs25}I've overstayed my welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你想呆多久就呆多久\N{\fs25}Nah. You can never overstay your welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是来带我回家的吗？\N{\fs25}You're here to take me home？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在就在家里\N{\fs25}This is home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,别把我丢在这儿 雷吉纳德\N{\fs25}Don't leave me here, Reginald.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈……\N{\fs25}Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 安德烈\N{\fs25}it's Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 是我 是小安\N{\fs25}It's Dre, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我得吃药了\N{\fs25}I need to take my meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 你吃过了\N{\fs25}No, no, no. You took them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经吃过了\N{\fs25}You already took them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很疲惫\N{\fs25}You look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你工作太辛苦了\N{\fs25}You work too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这点你倒是说的没错\N{\fs25}Yeah, you got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,工作嘛\N{\fs25}It's the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我干什么的\N{\fs25}It's what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs25}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你要勇于去直视恶魔\N{\fs25}You gotta look the devil in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 妈妈\N{\fs25}Yeah, Ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这里看起来跟你描述的别无二致\N{\fs25}Well, it looks just like you said it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 你的面罩闻起来像你胡子吗？\N{\fs25}Hey, does yours smell like your beard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不 像你的马子\N{\fs25}It smells like your girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,出发吧\N{\fs25}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是什么人\N{\fs25}Who the fuck are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是来取你可卡因的\N{\fs25}We're the guys that are taking your cocaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,傻得够呛 你们是来送死的\N{\fs25}Not smart. You guys are gonna fucking die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那玩意在哪儿？\N{\fs25}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,冷藏室 在楼下\N{\fs25}Freezer. Downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要钥匙吗？\N{\fs25}We need a key?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,来的就你们俩？\N{\fs25}Just two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚你们走不了了\N{\fs25}You're gonna be here all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！\N{\fs25}Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,走！\N{\fs25}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是三十公斤\N{\fs25}That's not 30 keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是三百公斤\N{\fs25}It's 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看来有人出了岔子\N{\fs25}Somebody fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 跪下\N{\fs25}Shut up. On your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fs25}Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这玩意儿是纯的\N{\fs25}This stuff hasn't been cut yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦吼！我们中头奖了！\N{\fs25}Jackpot! Fuck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没门 我们走\N{\fs25}No way. We walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么？ -我们走\N{\fs25}- What? - We walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你年龄小也有不机灵的时候\N{\fs25}Small ain't always smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你要么来搭把手 要么一边看着\N{\fs25}You can help or you can watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是蠢到家了\N{\fs25}This is fucking stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是自由\N{\fs25}This is fucking freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\fs25}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘\N{\fs25}Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙在哪儿？\N{\fs25}The fuck is this guy at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可能在后门那边 去看看\N{\fs25}He might be by the back door. Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}后边儿的车还没熄火{\i}\N{\fs25}{\i1}Car back here is still running.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}后门是开着的{\i}\N{\fs25}{\i1}Back gate open.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}可能在进行毒品交易{\i}\N{\fs25}{\i1}Possible 30 in progress.{\i}
