Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们 你们得起身离开\N{\fs25}Guys, I need you to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们坐的地方是犯罪现场\N{\fs25}You're sitting in my crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 别妨碍他办事\N{\fs25}Come on. He's got a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 凯利\N{\fs25}It's okay, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你今天去了内务局\N{\fs25}I heard you were with IA today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你明天能回来我会很开心的\N{\fs25}And I'd fucking love it if you were right back there tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们给我一个理由的话.\N{\fs25}If they give me cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,理由？\N{\fs25}Cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你该死的理由 可以吗？\N{\fs25}Here's your fucking cause right there. Okay?
