Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有七名警员横尸街头\N{\fs25}Your fucking cause times seven lying dead in the fucking street.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多理由够了吗\N{\fs25}Motherfuckers are giving you all the reason you need...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,麦肯 你不是唯一难过的人\N{\fs25}Mac! You're not the only one hurting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是公众场合\N{\fs25}You're in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,警员倒下时 公众什么都没看到.\N{\fs25}The public who never sees shit when a cop goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,声音轻点\N{\fs25}Lower your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们叫什么名字\N{\fs25}What were their names?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs25}Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,詹妮弗·蒙哥马利在救护车上.\N{\fs25}Jennifer Montgomery in the ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在命悬一线\N{\fs25}She's hanging on by a thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,马西莫·亚当斯 查理·科布.\N{\fs25}Massimo Adams, Charlie Cobb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克·多明格斯和丹尼·威廉姆斯\N{\fs25}Jake Dominguez and Danny Williams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,街上是马库斯·费尔南德斯.\N{\fs25}Out on the street is Marcus Fernandez.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,马库斯·费尔南德斯.\N{\fs25}Marcus Fernandez.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识马库斯.\N{\fs25}I knew Marcus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们上的同一所大学.\N{\fs25}We were at the academy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,和马库斯一起的\N{\fs25}Out there with Marcus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是鲁本·基泽和帕特里克·格雷厄姆.\N{\fs25}is Reuben Kizer and Patrick Graham.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所知\N{\fs25}Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们留下了四个遗孀\N{\fs25}they leave behind four wives,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一个未婚妻 \N{\fs25}one fiancée,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,和六个孩子.\N{\fs25}six kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其中三个还是我的教子.\N{\fs25}Three are my godkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在不得不在半夜叫醒他们 \N{\fs25}Now I'm gonna go wake them up in the middle of the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们这个天塌般的噩耗\N{\fs25}let them know their lives are shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道演练吗\N{\fs25}You know the drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你 \N{\fs25}Look, I fucking refuse
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会因为审判上诉 \N{\fs25}to allow these families to be traumatized even more
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,假释听证会和某些不着边际的陈述\N{\fs25}with fucking trials and appeals and horseshit narratives,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,让这些家庭遭受更多的创伤了\N{\fs25}parole hearings for, fuck, three, four decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我在请求你\N{\fs25}I'm asking you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,保护他们免遭这些事情的伤害\N{\fs25}to protect them from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白.\N{\fs25}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么在这儿？\N{\fs25}Why were they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人刚防范了一宗抢劫案.\N{\fs25}My guys interrupted a robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有多少可卡因？\N{\fs25}How much cocaine is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人渣给毒品提纯之前\N{\fs25}Crime Scene estimates about 300 kilos
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,犯罪现场估计有300公斤可卡因.\N{\fs25}before the scumbags cut into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拿走了多少？\N{\fs25}How much did they take?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:21:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多50公斤\N{\fs25}About 50 keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,110磅.\N{\fs25}One hundred and ten pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那是A1的重量 你看的是25年的\N{\fs25}That's A1 weight. You're looking at 25 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,纯度超过九成.\N{\fs25}Ninety-plus percent pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,两百万左右 在你来之前\N{\fs25}Two million, plus or minus, before you step on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,之后是四倍\N{\fs25}It's quadruple after.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈·戴维斯警探 这位是弗兰基·伯恩斯 缉毒局的 \N{\fs25}Detective Andre Davis, Detective Frankie Burns, DETF.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-她将与你一起共事  -和我干嘛？\N{\fs25}- She'll be working with you. - With me doing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我目前所知最大的一次检获\N{\fs25}This is the biggest coke seizure in I don't know how long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-将涉及毒品  -我很感激这项政策\N{\fs25}- Narcotics will be involved. - I appreciate the politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,未来3到4个小时如果我不能将这帮暴徒绳之于法 就再也抓不到了\N{\fs25}But if I don't catch these guys in the next three or four hours, they vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是政策\N{\fs25}I don't do fucking politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她和我们是一队的\N{\fs25}And she's not the second team.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.98,0:22:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以和我唱反调 也可以与我合作\N{\fs25}You can either fight me or use me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.55,0:23:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\N{\fs25}You good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该以死谢罪\N{\fs25}We should fucking kill ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.82,0:23:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,别那样 现在不是时候\N{\fs25}Don't be like that. Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,雷 我们不知杀了多少个警察\N{\fs25}We just killed more cops than I can fucking count, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我杀的\N{\fs25}I did all the killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为他们不会在乎尸体数量吗？\N{\fs25}You think they give a shit about the body math?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会发现我们的.\N{\fs25}They're gonna figure us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,天很黑 我们行动迅速 车子不是我们的 车牌也是偷来的\N{\fs25}It was dark. We moved fast. Car's not ours. Plates are stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.32,0:23:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,迟早会败露的 雷 好吗\N{\fs25}It'll get solved, Ray. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都很讨厌条子 但不得不承认他们很聪明\N{\fs25}We both hate the fucking cops, but they're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,天亮前他们就能查出我们 我们得赶紧跑路\N{\fs25}They're gonna figure out our names by sunrise. We need to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得定个计划 我们需要钱\N{\fs25}We need a plan. We need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,该死！\N{\fs25}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是员工？\N{\fs25}Employee?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对的 从后方潜入\N{\fs25}Yeah. Came up whistle-clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这个丧命的好市民叫汤姆·切弗\N{\fs25}No-scroll good citizen named Tom Cheaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆是近距离中弹的\N{\fs25}So, Tom took his bullet from just a few feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,注意伤口周围的点\N{\fs25}Notice the stippling around the entrance wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.85,0:23:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,从那把刀的位置判断 \N{\fs25}And judging from the proximity of that knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆打算偷袭\N{\fs25}Tom tried to make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 \N{\fs25}Over here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.75,0:23:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,两次击发\N{\fs25}double taps.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,自动式压制武器 \N{\fs25}Automatic weapon, suppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我说有两个枪手\N{\fs25}I say two shooters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看出来的\N{\fs25}Where are you seeing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.92,0:23:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人不可能轻松解决掉这么多警察\N{\fs25}No one's smooth enough to murder all these officers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.82,0:23:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还要杀死拿刀偷袭的汤姆\N{\fs25}and hit Tom coming up with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人也不可能独自携带100多磅的可卡因\N{\fs25}And one guy probably isn't carrying 100-plus pounds of cocaine out by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.09,0:24:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 但也可能不止两个\N{\fs25}Yeah, but it could be more than two.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.82,0:24:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不 看一下弹壳分布\N{\fs25}Nah. Look at the shell groupings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一人在后面 解决了汤姆\N{\fs25}One was back there. He hit Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.32,0:24:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个人就从这边过来\N{\fs25}The second one came this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,然后杀害了四个警员\N{\fs25}Then he murdered all four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.38,0:24:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,第二个杀手很厉害\N{\fs25}Second one's a talented killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.02,0:24:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你少说了一个零 混蛋\N{\fs25}You left a zero off, motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.42,0:24:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不止30公斤\N{\fs25}That wasn't 30 keys stepped on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.59,0:24:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是300公斤纯的\N{\fs25}It was 300 pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.32,0:24:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不能怪我\N{\fs25}Wasn't my fuckup.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.49,0:24:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那怪谁\N{\fs25}Whose fuckup was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.99,0:24:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怪霍克·泰勒吧 那家伙把活分包出去的\N{\fs25}Hawk Tyler's, maybe? He put the job out for bid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.12,0:24:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们也有货对吗？\N{\fs25}But you guys got something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.12,0:24:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-有50公斤  -好的\N{\fs25}- Fifty keys. - Well, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.85,0:24:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-去你的  -交易得改改了\N{\fs25}- Fuck you! - I'm changing the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.72,0:24:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用替我们卖货了.\N{\fs25}You're not selling it for us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.62,0:24:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你带我们去见霍克 我们把货直接卖给他.\N{\fs25}You're gonna bring us to Hawk, and we're gonna sell it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.22,0:24:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不需要第三方销货\N{\fs25}And we're not splitting it three ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.52,0:24:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我欠了一屁股外债\N{\fs25}I owe a lot of money to a lot of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.49,0:25:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我和雷下半辈子得跑路了！\N{\fs25}Me and Ray have to run for the rest of our fucking lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.09,0:25:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,霍克不会接受新交易的\N{\fs25}Hawk ain't gonna hear new deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.82,0:25:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,的确 可是霍克也不知道我们有50公斤高纯度的可卡因啊.\N{\fs25}Yeah, well, Hawk hasn't heard 50 pure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.32,0:25:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把电话给我.\N{\fs25}Give me your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.22,0:25:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,发现目标\N{\fs25}Hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.82,0:25:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发现目标了\N{\fs25}We got a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.29,0:25:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这是红灯摄像头拍到的\N{\fs25}It's a red light cam.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.35,0:25:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,两个人.\N{\fs25}Two men.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.19,0:25:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,通知大家 把照片发送给莫斯托的警方\N{\fs25}Alert everybody. Send it through the mobile unit at Mosto's.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.29,0:25:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,戴维斯警探.\N{\fs25}Detective Davis.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.95,0:25:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是约兰达·贝尔中士 身份识别中心的值班主管\N{\fs25}Sergeant Yolanda Bell, shift supervisor at LMSI.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.65,0:25:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很高心认识你 约兰达·贝尔.\N{\fs25}Good to know you, Yolanda Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.69,0:25:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们有东西给你.{\i}\N{\fs25}{\i1}We got something for you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.25,0:25:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你想赌多少 我赌找到那辆宝马时已经烧得只剩底盘了\N{\fs25}How much you wanna bet when we find that BMW, it's burnt to the chassis?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.92,0:26:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钱\N{\fs25}A nickel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.12,0:26:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要抢劫660磅的可卡因.\N{\fs25}If you were gonna rob 660 pounds of coke,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.66,0:26:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你会开一辆双门宝马轿车去抢劫吗？\N{\fs25}would you drive a BMW two-door to the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.25,0:26:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只带一个同伙？\N{\fs25}Would you bring just one other guy with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.25,0:26:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,还只抢50公斤？\N{\fs25}Would you only take 50 keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.92,0:26:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,都不可能\N{\fs25}No, no, and no.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.59,0:26:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没想到会有300公斤\N{\fs25}They weren't expecting 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.32,0:26:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也没有想到会有警察\N{\fs25}They weren't expecting cops, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.29,0:26:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要么是他们倒霉\N{\fs25}This was either dumb luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.69,0:26:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要么是圈套\N{\fs25}or a setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.42,0:26:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 草泥马！\N{\fs25}No, fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.86,0:26:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI来这是因为\N{\fs25}The FBI's here because the shooters
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.35,0:26:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手已经跑了\N{\fs25}are out of the state by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.59,0:26:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,离最后的枪声已经过去了半个小时了\N{\fs25}Half hour since the final whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.99,0:26:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,请等我们再找到一个目击线索\N{\fs25}Please, make one more sports analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.39,0:26:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们得到确认\N{\fs25}If and when we get confirmation
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.92,0:26:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手已经跑到新泽西或者康乃狄克州...\N{\fs25}that they crossed over to cor Connecticut...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.82,0:26:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,市长比较倾向于FBI接手这个案子越快越好\N{\fs25}The mayor would prefer that the FBI take over sooner than later.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.09,0:26:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,市长一有机会就贬低我们\N{\fs25}The mayor shits on us every chance he gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.76,0:26:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他都不算真正的纽约人\N{\fs25}The fucking guy eats pizza with a fork.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.25,0:26:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他希望这些人被绳之以法\N{\fs25}He wants them brought to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.69,0:26:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,放屁\N{\fs25}No shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.29,0:26:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,德烈\N{\fs25}Dre.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.49,0:26:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,特万\N{\fs25}Toine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.96,0:26:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,内务局那边怎么样？\N{\fs25}How'd it go with Internal Affairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.59,0:27:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这了 所以不是你希望的那样\N{\fs25}I'm here, so not the way you hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.79,0:27:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,和我之前说的一样 市长想将他们绳之以法\N{\fs25}Like I said, the mayor wants them brought to justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.32,0:27:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,比如逮捕 提起诉讼 接受审判\N{\fs25}i.e., arrested, arraigned, put on trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.69,0:27:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是乱枪击毙 细节就不多说了\N{\fs25}Not killed in a gun battle, the details of which are foggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.59,0:27:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我们牺牲的那七位？\N{\fs25}Like the seven behind us?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.96,0:27:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你是哪位？缉毒警\N{\fs25}Who are you? Narcotics.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.76,0:27:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,完美 简直一应俱全 一个是缉毒刑警 一个喜欢开枪\N{\fs25}Beautiful. What could go wrong? We got a narc and a trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.69,0:27:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你说话最好好听点 什么叫“喜欢开枪”\N{\fs25}You better have perfect diction, calling me a "trigger."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.59,0:27:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都别吵了\N{\fs25}Cut the shit, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.99,0:27:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,市长赞同这件事吗？\N{\fs25}Has the mayor got his thumb on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.66,0:27:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是请求还是命令？\N{\fs25}This an ask or an order?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.86,0:27:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还在纽约\N{\fs25}They're still in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.76,0:27:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有人拿着50公斤九成纯度的可卡因跑路的\N{\fs25}You don't walk away with 50 keys of 90% pure
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.26,0:27:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,除非他有当地的大客户\N{\fs25}unless you have a big local buyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.99,0:27:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你有运输工具否则不会把毒品带远\N{\fs25}You don't move it far unless you're into transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.09,0:27:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙是打手 不是司机\N{\fs25}These guys were hitters, not drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.59,0:27:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你并不能确定\N{\fs25}You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.66,0:27:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可以干掉七个警察\N{\fs25}Good enough to kill seven cops,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.52,0:27:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,却又蠢到去闯红灯吗？\N{\fs25}dumb enough to run a red?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.99,0:27:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们需要做的是卖掉可卡因 然后消失\N{\fs25}What they need to do is sell the coke, vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.29,0:27:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会去东边\N{\fs25}I'm not heading east.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.39,0:27:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,往长岛方向跑\N{\fs25}Long Island runs out,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.42,0:27:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是会计\N{\fs25}and it's all accountants
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.62,0:27:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,和牙医\N{\fs25}and dentists out that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.72,0:27:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我有那么多货\N{\fs25}so I'm a sore thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.59,0:27:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不会去皇后区的\N{\fs25}I'm not going to Queens.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.99,0:27:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,中产阶级是不会买那么多可卡因的\N{\fs25}You don't wholesale coke in the middle class.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.02,0:27:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会呆在布鲁克林这个不法之地\N{\fs25}I'm not staying in Brooklyn, scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.19,0:27:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,加上现在全是像你一样的便衣和巡警\N{\fs25}Plus, it's all pop-ups and strollers and guys like you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.59,0:27:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,斯塔滕岛上还有谁能这么快的运送毒品呢？\N{\fs25}Anyone left on Staten Island who can move this kind of weight as quick as they need?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.32,0:28:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在黑帮大佬戈蒂杀了卡斯特拉诺之后就没有人了\N{\fs25}Not since the days before Gotti murdered Castellano.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.09,0:28:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,新泽西州呢？\N{\fs25}What about Jersey?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.16,0:28:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,《黑道家族》是个电视剧\N{\fs25}"Sopranos" was a TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.62,0:28:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,上城区呢？ 那是扯淡\N{\fs25}And upstate? That's fucking ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.82,0:28:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没有办法能在尤蒂卡运送50公斤毒品\N{\fs25}Ain't no way to move 50 keys of yayo in Utica.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.42,0:28:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩下曼哈顿了\N{\fs25}Leaves Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.62,0:28:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,戴维斯警探\N{\fs25}Detective Davis?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.09,0:28:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 找到线索了吗\N{\fs25}What, you got a hit for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.39,0:28:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,收到报警电话\N{\fs25}911 call.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.39,0:28:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有辆黑色双门宝马\N{\fs25}Black BMW, two-door,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.72,0:28:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在中国城被烧了\N{\fs25}on fire in an alley in Chinatown.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.49,0:28:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 哪个中国城？\N{\fs25}Uh-oh, where's Chinatown?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.49,0:28:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,曼哈顿的\N{\fs25}Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.82,0:28:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-感觉不错？ -确实\N{\fs25}- Feel good? - It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.66,0:28:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-多久以前的来电？ -一分半以前\N{\fs25}- How long ago was the 911? - Ninety seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.42,0:28:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们走  -等一下\N{\fs25}- Let's go. - Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.39,0:28:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-还等什么  -关于他们的信息 \N{\fs25}- For what? - Everything about these guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.93,0:28:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,除了测速摄像以外 我们知道的太少了\N{\fs25}save the speed camera, has been competent so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.96,0:28:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢？他们会卖了可卡因 接着赶火车 \N{\fs25}Yeah, so? They'll sell the coke, catch a train,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.79,0:28:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,搭出租 抢辆车 \N{\fs25}catch a cab, jack a car,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.42,0:28:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在这里希望能通过摄像头找到他们\N{\fs25}and we're right back to hoping we get a hit from a cam
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.46,0:28:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在他们消失并出现在宾夕法尼亚州之前\N{\fs25}before they vanish, show up in Pennsylvania somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.86,0:28:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有道理  不过FBI是全国...\N{\fs25}Good point. Whereas the FBI is national...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.22,0:28:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,封锁这个岛\N{\fs25}Close the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.06,0:28:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个岛？\N{\fs25}What island?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.13,0:28:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,曼哈顿岛\N{\fs25}Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.13,0:28:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗？\N{\fs25}You having a seizure?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.43,0:28:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不 市长会同意的\N{\fs25}No, the mayor will buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.92,0:28:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在才30多岁 犯罪率在上升\N{\fs25}He's in the low 30s, crime is ticking up,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.99,0:28:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,无家可归的人在蒂芙尼店门口撒尿 \N{\fs25}homeless are pissing in front of Tiffany's again,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.23,0:29:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是凌晨一点 不是下午一点\N{\fs25}and it's 1:00 a.m., not 1:00 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.83,0:29:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果出现意外 我们背锅\N{\fs25}Anything goes wrong, you can blame us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.43,0:29:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果出事你们就惨了\N{\fs25}Something will go wrong, and then you're all fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.53,0:29:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道FBI不懂牺牲就像不懂量子力学一样\N{\fs25}We get the concept of sacrifice is like quantum physics to a fucking fed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.43,0:29:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,市长可以说是他听从了实战指挥官的意见\N{\fs25}The mayor can say he was listening to his commanders in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.96,0:29:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 如果你们上司有机会\N{\fs25}Now, if your boss had a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.49,0:29:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,能抓住杀了七个纽约警察的凶手\N{\fs25}to catch the murderers of seven New York City cops
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.56,0:29:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但不去做 这个城市不会原谅他的\N{\fs25}and chose not to, this city would never forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.76,0:29:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,5点之前抓住他们\N{\fs25}Catch them by 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.46,0:29:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 你们这是同意了吗？\N{\fs25}Wait, is that a yes or a no?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.79,0:29:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,5点之前抓住他们\N{\fs25}Catch them by 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.56,0:29:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都有胆量\N{\fs25}You all got balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.49,0:29:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是差点头脑\N{\fs25}not a lot of brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.49,0:29:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你们好运\N{\fs25}Good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.09,0:29:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会等你们电话的\N{\fs25}We'll be awaiting your phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.66,0:29:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 屏息以待吧\N{\fs25}Yeah, hold your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.33,0:29:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么做？\N{\fs25}How you gonna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.39,0:29:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,曼哈顿有21座桥 全部封锁\N{\fs25}There are 21 bridges in and out of Manhattan. Shut them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.59,0:30:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,三条河 全部关闭  四条隧道 全部堵住\N{\fs25}Three rivers, close them. Four tunnels, block them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.59,0:30:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,把所有出岛的火车都拦住 特拉克 PATH 新泽西运输公司 \N{\fs25}Stop every train that leaves the island. Amtrak, PATH, New Jersey Transit,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.53,0:30:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,长岛铁路 北地铁 还有环线地铁\N{\fs25}LIRR, Metro-North, and loop the subways.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.63,0:30:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,然后...\N{\fs25}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.63,0:30:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们全岛展开搜索\N{\fs25}we flood the island with blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.13,0:31:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人想弃车 就要先开出五条街以外去 别扔在曼哈顿\N{\fs25}You wanna ditch a car, you drive five blocks, not to Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.93,0:31:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,两组轮胎印\N{\fs25}Two sets of tire tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.19,0:31:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有场碰面\N{\fs25}This was a meet-and-greet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.10,0:31:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,约兰达女士\N{\fs25}Miss Yolanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.16,0:31:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我需要所有在宝马之后进入巷子的车的照片\N{\fs25}Hey, I need pictures of every car that went into the alley after the BMW.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.83,0:31:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}入口处没有摄像头\N{\fs25}There aren't any cameras aimed right at the entrances.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.60,0:31:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,巷子深处是按摩店和中餐馆\N{\fs25}Alley backs up into massage parlors and Chinese restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.90,0:31:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是非法劳工 只要一安上摄像头 就会被毁坏\N{\fs25}It's illegal workers. Every time a camera goes up, it gets pulled back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.60,0:31:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你能找出开过巷子两侧的所有车吗\N{\fs25}Can you pick up every passing vehicle on either end?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.93,0:31:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}什么时间段？\N{\fs25}What interval?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.30,0:31:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,从宝马进入巷子之后\N{\fs25}From the time the BMW went into the alley
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.53,0:31:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,到有人报警发现火情的时候\N{\fs25}to the first fire call to 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.33,0:31:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 稍等\N{\fs25}Will do. Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.80,0:31:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你是他们说的那个人吗？\N{\fs25}Are you who they say you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.73,0:31:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说我是谁？\N{\fs25}Who do they say I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.00,0:31:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你来告诉我\N{\fs25}You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.46,0:32:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你过去十年杀了好多人\N{\fs25}You killed a lot of perps in the last ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.43,0:32:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,都是自卫才杀的\N{\fs25}Never shot first.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.80,0:32:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,从没主动杀过人？\N{\fs25}Never?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.06,0:32:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 让我说更具体一些 伯恩斯警官\N{\fs25}All right, let me be more precise, Detective Burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.16,0:32:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没有正当理由我是不会开枪的\N{\fs25}I've never fired without just cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.00,0:32:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为七个警察报仇感觉就是正当理由\N{\fs25}Seven dead cops feels like a lot of just cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.23,0:32:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是杀手\N{\fs25}These guys are killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.13,0:32:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我要确保今天晚上我们能互相照应\N{\fs25}So I need to know that we got each other's backs tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.43,0:32:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我家里还有个孩子\N{\fs25}'Cause I got a kid at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.80,0:32:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她醒来不能没有母亲\N{\fs25}Doesn't need to wake up without her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.80,0:32:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是警察 我会照应你的\N{\fs25}You wear that badge, I got your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.33,0:32:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,请讲\N{\fs25}Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.90,0:32:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs25}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.23,0:32:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去哪？ 上城区\N{\fs25}Where we going? Uptown.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.60,0:32:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...已经封锁曼哈顿了\N{\fs25}...has closed all access into and out of Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.07,0:32:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在市政厅的声明中 市长办公室只能{\i}\N{\fs25}{\i1}In a statement from city hall, the mayor's office was only able to offer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.23,0:33:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对两名嫌疑犯作模糊的描述\N{\fs25}{\i1}a vague description of the two suspects.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.00,0:33:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们告知两人都是男性 一白一黑\N{\fs25}{\i1}They tell us both are men. One is white, one is black.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.80,0:33:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们携带武器 十分危险\N{\fs25}{\i1}They are known to be armed and extremely dangerous.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.13,0:33:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,副市长安东尼·摩特支持封锁曼哈顿\N{\fs25}{\i1}Deputy Mayor Antoine Mott defends the decision to lock down the city.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.63,0:33:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他的原话是 “这两名歹徒已无路可逃\N{\fs25}{\i1}His statement says, "With no way off the island for these two fugitives,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.10,0:33:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,现已出动纽约全部警力……\N{\fs25}{\i1}the NYPD has every available...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.97,0:33:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-是好货  -全力搜索曼哈顿”\N{\fs25}- Nice. - {\i1}...officer scouring Manhattan.{\i}"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.50,0:33:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有多少？\N{\fs25}How much have you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.47,0:33:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,五十公斤\N{\fs25}Fifty kilos.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.47,0:33:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...直到成功完成这次搜索\N{\fs25}..."until this manhunt is successfully completed."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.53,0:33:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好 兄弟  -你好\N{\fs25}- What up, B? - What up?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.53,0:33:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这事太不寻常了\N{\fs25}This ain't usual and customary.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.27,0:33:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚没有事情寻常\N{\fs25}Nothing is tonight, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.50,0:33:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是雷·杰克逊\N{\fs25}This is Ray Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.97,0:33:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是迈克尔...\N{\fs25}And this is Michael...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.27,0:33:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你出的价是30公斤的\N{\fs25}The bid you put out was for 30 keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.43,0:33:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,实际却是300公斤\N{\fs25}We walked in on 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.63,0:33:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,难免有突发情况  对么\N{\fs25}Sometimes lightning strikes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.43,0:33:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全置身事外简直再好不过了\N{\fs25}And even better when you're a borough away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.67,0:33:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 的确如此\N{\fs25}Yeah, most definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.27,0:33:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我们杀了警察  一辈子都要逃亡\N{\fs25}Look, we killed cops, and now we gotta run forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.43,0:34:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那就带着你的讨价还价  滚上你的逃亡之旅吧  还有要说的么？\N{\fs25}Then get on with your negotiations and fuck your little guilt trip, word?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.67,0:34:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个抢竞争对手货的毒贩\N{\fs25}I'm a drug dealer who hit a rival drug dealer,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.53,0:34:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而你们就是给我干脏活的人\N{\fs25}and you're the guns I got to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.93,0:34:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你们认为我耍了你们  就因为有人少说了一个零？\N{\fs25}You think I fucked you because someone somewhere forgot a zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.03,0:34:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不跟那些斤斤计较的混蛋交易\N{\fs25}Our business doesn't attract a lot of detail-oriented motherfuckers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.13,0:34:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你看不惯  自己干\N{\fs25}You don't like it, make your own moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.13,0:34:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要么打车走人  要么咱们成交\N{\fs25}Or go drive an Uber. Either way, let's make this deal
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.47,0:34:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我就能以最快的速度\N{\fs25}so I can get you America's Most Wanted motherfuckers
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.60,0:34:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,把你们两个头号通缉犯从我的住所赶出去\N{\fs25}out of my crib fast as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.37,0:34:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,100万\N{\fs25}One million.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.10,0:34:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,比索？\N{\fs25}Pesos?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.70,0:34:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,呦！我就喜欢有货还不懂行情的傻瓜\N{\fs25}Yo! I love it when fools strike gold but don't know the market price.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.80,0:34:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,50公斤分200份\N{\fs25}Fifty keys cuts into 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.17,0:34:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,曼哈顿每份市场价是3万2\N{\fs25}Going rate for a cut key in Manhattan is 32 G's.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.23,0:34:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说给我们100万后\N{\fs25}That means after a million to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.90,0:34:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你还剩540万\N{\fs25}that's still 5.4 million for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.77,0:34:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是那些斤斤计较的混蛋之一\N{\fs25}He's one of those detail-oriented motherfuckers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.47,0:35:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,警察！别动！搜查令！\N{\fs25}Police! Don't move! Search warrant!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.90,0:35:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,左边！\N{\fs25}To the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.07,0:35:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,警察！举起手来！\N{\fs25}Police! Show me your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.33,0:35:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,转过来！\N{\fs25}Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.47,0:35:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  干什么！\N{\fs25}Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.47,0:35:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N{\fs25}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.40,0:35:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,放开他！不！他什么都没做！\N{\fs25}Get off of him! No, he didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.63,0:35:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能呼吸了！\N{\fs25}He can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.70,0:35:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是把他杀了\N{\fs25}You know if you kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.00,0:35:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他就什么都不能告诉我们了\N{\fs25}he can't tell us anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.44,0:35:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-站起来 过来  -好的\N{\fs25}- Stand up. Step over here. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.67,0:35:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？这是你的车吗？\N{\fs25}What's going on? Is this you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.17,0:35:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-不 这不是我的车  -可它登记在你名下\N{\fs25}- No, that is not my car. - It's registered in your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.77,0:35:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是我前男友的 他的信用不好  所以登记在了我名下\N{\fs25}My ex-boyfriend, he had terrible credit, so I put it in my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.67,0:35:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他把车卖了！\N{\fs25}He said he sold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.84,0:35:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-他说谎  -他一直都说谎\N{\fs25}- He lied. - All the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.07,0:35:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你打错人了！\N{\fs25}You beat up the wrong man!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.57,0:35:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会有事\N{\fs25}He'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.64,0:35:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把他带走\N{\fs25}Get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.77,0:35:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fs25}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.27,0:35:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你还好吗？\N{\fs25}Hey. You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.14,0:35:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,转过来\N{\fs25}Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.50,0:35:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,奥  天\N{\fs25}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.00,0:35:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 住手\N{\fs25}Knock it off. Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.44,0:35:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系\N{\fs25}It's all right. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.04,0:36:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 你的前男友...\N{\fs25}So, this ex-boyfriend of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.70,0:36:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,托里亚诺·布什\N{\fs25}Toriano Bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.44,0:36:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-他犯了什么事  -今晚死了7个警察\N{\fs25}- What'd he do now? - Seven cops were murdered tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.84,0:36:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-啊 不是托里亚诺做的  -他安排了这两个人\N{\fs25}- Well, Toriano didn't do that. - He picked up these two men.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.80,0:36:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为他们是凶手\N{\fs25}We think they're the murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.10,0:36:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这两个人迄今还没找到\N{\fs25}There isn't a version of this where these two aren't found.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.77,0:36:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在请你配合\N{\fs25}Cooperate now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.24,0:36:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我一些我不知道的事情\N{\fs25}Tell me something I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.74,0:36:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,说完我们立马离开\N{\fs25}and that's the beginning of the end of our time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.80,0:36:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  托里亚诺是不会杀人的\N{\fs25}Toriano couldn't kill anyone, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.67,0:36:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过了 但他犯过罪 是吗\N{\fs25}You said that. But he's a criminal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.10,0:36:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一些小罪 想赚钱脱身 他总是深陷债务\N{\fs25}Small-time. Wanted to get out. He was always just too deep in debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.50,0:36:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你离开了他？\N{\fs25}Is that why you left him?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.30,0:36:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是因为债务离开的\N{\fs25}Debt don't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.34,0:36:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那勾引他的小三是谁\N{\fs25}Who was Becky with the good hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.60,0:36:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她是泛美酒吧的服务员\N{\fs25}This waitress ho at the Pan-Am.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.40,0:36:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-去查查  -谢谢\N{\fs25}- Check it. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.77,0:36:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,坐\N{\fs25}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.27,0:36:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你回避一下\N{\fs25}Give us a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.20,0:37:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 约兰达 把托里亚诺·布什的所有信息都给我\N{\fs25}Hey, Yolanda, get me everything you have on Toriano Bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.10,0:37:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,调一下泛美酒吧附近的监控\N{\fs25}And get cameras up and around the Pan-Am Lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.64,0:37:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他女朋友在那里\N{\fs25}He has a girlfriend there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.74,0:37:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}收到{\i}\N{\fs25}{\i1}Got it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.94,0:37:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,每捆一百张？\N{\fs25}You have it in hundreds?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.17,0:37:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们花美元\N{\fs25}Brown people spend Benjamins,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.67,0:37:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,会被追踪\N{\fs25}brown people get followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.11,0:37:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,与可卡因一样重\N{\fs25}Weighs as much as the coke.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.44,0:37:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的对\N{\fs25}You about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.54,0:37:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一百万在20年代相当于110英镑\N{\fs25}A million in 20s is 110 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.87,0:37:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 离警犬远点儿\N{\fs25}And stay away from all canines.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.20,0:37:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,缉毒犬能闻到钞票上沾有可卡因的气味\N{\fs25}They go {\i1}Cujo{\i} because every dollar in circulation is covered in cocaine atoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.60,0:37:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,并且  你们那6个小包中总共有5万钞票\N{\fs25}and y'all got 50,000 of those bills in six small bags.
