Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.30,0:57:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔 看着我\N{\fs25}Michael, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.00,0:57:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-别耍花招  -没人耍花招\N{\fs25}- Don't fuck with me! - Nobody's fucking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.54,0:58:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但事实是 你打死了她 我会同时杀了你\N{\fs25}But facts: You shoot her, I'm gonna kill you in the same breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.90,0:58:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那你所知道的一切就都化为乌有了\N{\fs25}And everything you think you know or may have means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.74,0:58:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以放下枪 我们一起看看驱动器里都有什么\N{\fs25}So drop your weapon, and let's take a look at the drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.74,0:58:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  我做不到\N{\fs25}No. No, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.43,0:58:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-迈克尔 你需要相信我   -我不信任何人\N{\fs25}- Michael, I need you to trust me. - I don't trust anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.60,0:58:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有选择了\N{\fs25}You have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.90,0:58:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,即使开放城市 你也是插翅难逃\N{\fs25}You're not gonna escape to some island somewhere, even after they open this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.77,0:58:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你那么聪明应该明白这点\N{\fs25}You're smart enough to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.47,0:58:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我 嗯？\N{\fs25}I am, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.94,0:58:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这世界你已经无处可藏了\N{\fs25}The world's just gonna keep closing in on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.07,0:58:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但只要你束手就擒 就能挺过这一劫\N{\fs25}But you can survive this if you just give yourself up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.87,0:58:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不！迈克尔！\N{\fs25}No! Michael!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.87,0:58:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs25}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.47,0:58:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\N{\fs25}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.14,0:58:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？\N{\fs25}What the fuck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.74,0:59:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我是戴维斯\N{\fs25}This is Davis.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.94,0:59:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,封锁七个街区的范围\N{\fs25}Lock down everything in a seven-block radius
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.30,0:59:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就以维切尔牛肉店为中心\N{\fs25}from Weichsel Beef's center of the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.07,0:59:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我确认迈克尔·特鲁希略90秒前从这离开\N{\fs25}Positive ID on Michael Trujillo leaving there 90 seconds ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.40,0:59:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,特鲁希略有对此案至关重要的信息\N{\fs25}Trujillo has information vital to this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.64,0:59:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只许活捉\N{\fs25}He must be brought in alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.64,0:59:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-让我看看  -我没事\N{\fs25}- Let me see. - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.24,0:59:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好 你当心\N{\fs25}Yeah, you look it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.84,0:59:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道那驱动器里都有什么\N{\fs25}I wanna know what's on those drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.77,0:59:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,控制中心 通知84号单位建立防线\N{\fs25}{\i1}Central, advise the units that are 84 to set up a perimeter{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.60,0:59:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,从西12街到西19街 从第八大道到水边\N{\fs25}{\i1}from West 12th Street to West 19th and from Eighth Avenue to the water.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.84,0:59:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不准任何人进出\N{\fs25}{\i1}No one in or out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.14,1:00:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？你能相信吗？\N{\fs25}What? Can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.54,1:00:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,恶心 很恶心\N{\fs25}Disgusting. It's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.77,1:00:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,游泳池在26楼\N{\fs25}And the pool is on the 26th floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.41,1:01:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘\N{\fs25}Shh!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.41,1:01:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不出声 我就不会伤害你\N{\fs25}I won't hurt you if you stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.24,1:01:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吗\N{\fs25}You got it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.07,1:01:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,知道就点头\N{\fs25}Nod.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.41,1:01:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs25}Shit. Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.31,1:01:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑密码是什么\N{\fs25}What's the password?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.47,1:01:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs25}Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.74,1:01:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eightclap1\N{\fs25}"Eightclap1."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.61,1:01:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要把“eight”拼写出来\N{\fs25}Gotta spell the word "eight."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.41,1:01:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,1是数字\N{\fs25}One is the number.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.01,1:01:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没空格？嗯\N{\fs25}One word? Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.57,1:01:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛\N{\fs25}Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.35,1:02:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么没开枪？\N{\fs25}Why didn't you shoot him?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.92,1:02:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们告诉我你无所畏惧\N{\fs25}They told me you were fearless.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.18,1:02:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,说你是手刃警察杀手的人\N{\fs25}The guy who kills cop killers.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.62,1:02:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是想知道真相 就这样\N{\fs25}I just need the truth, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.48,1:02:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信一个警察杀手的话？\N{\fs25}You believe a cop killer?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.25,1:02:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好 凯利  休息一下\N{\fs25}Good work, Kelly. Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.42,1:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你干掉了一个恶棍\N{\fs25}You took down one vicious son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.15,1:02:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 可惜没在他杀害无辜平民之前\N{\fs25}Yeah, not before he killed an innocent civilian.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.68,1:02:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你为世界铲除了一颗老鼠屎\N{\fs25}World's a better place with that guy gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.75,1:02:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你看过他的档案吗？\N{\fs25}You seen his record?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.35,1:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄了一眼\N{\fs25}Glanced at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.49,1:03:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道找你负责是对的\N{\fs25}I knew I had the right guy for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.75,1:03:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,各司其职 不是吗\N{\fs25}All hands on deck, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.45,1:03:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是你们的人把他们从公寓里赶出来的\N{\fs25}It was your boys who smoked them out of this apartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.42,1:03:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,凯利警官怎么这么快就找到这了？\N{\fs25}How did Lieutenant Kelly even get here so quick?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.65,1:03:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这乱的\N{\fs25}Look at this fucking mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.92,1:03:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-仍然有一个在逃的 对吗？  -是的\N{\fs25}- You still got one guy on the run, right? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.49,1:03:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,已经早上4:37了\N{\fs25}It's 4:37 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.32,1:03:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在我开放曼哈顿之前 你只有不到一个小时了\N{\fs25}You've got less than an hour before I gotta open the island.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.25,1:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你那时还没抓到他 可就回天乏术了\N{\fs25}You haven't gotten him by then, we're all eating shit for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.52,1:03:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不要担心那个在逃犯\N{\fs25}Don't worry about the other perp.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.08,1:03:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈已经把他封锁在七个街区的范围内了\N{\fs25}Andre put that motherfucker in a seven-block box.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.19,1:03:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他快超过时限了\N{\fs25}He's on borrowed time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.75,1:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔·特鲁希略仍不知所踪\N{\fs25}{\i1}Michael Trujillo is still at large,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.95,1:04:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但警方认为他被困在肉库区的某个地方\N{\fs25}{\i1}but police believe he is surrounded somewhere inside the Meatpacking District.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.15,1:04:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,市长办公室表扬了纽约警察局官员\N{\fs25}{\i1}The mayor's office has praised NYPD officers{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.92,1:04:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢他们在追捕过程中取得的进展\N{\fs25}{\i1}for the progress they've made in this manhunt.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.29,1:04:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,副市长安东尼·摩特\N{\fs25}{\i1}Deputy Mayor Antoine Mott had this to say{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.32,1:04:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在刚才的新闻发布会上说\N{\fs25}{\i1}in a press briefing just moments ago.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.79,1:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,德拉姆市长缩短了他对欧盟的贸易访问\N{\fs25}{\i1}Mayor Drum cut short his trade mission to the EU{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.39,1:04:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经在从布鲁塞尔回国的飞机上了\N{\fs25}{\i1}and is already on a plane home from Brussels.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.99,1:04:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请我转达他对本市市民的谢意\N{\fs25}{\i1}Asked me to pass along his gratitude to the citizens of this city.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.72,1:04:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他说 “纽约市民是世界上最棒的” \N{\fs25}{\i1}"World's greatest," his words.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.95,1:04:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你们的耐心和帮助\N{\fs25}{\i1}Without your patience and assistance,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.12,1:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要补充一点 德拉姆市长大胆的想法\N{\fs25}{\i1}and, I'll add, the boldness of Mayor Drum's idea{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.62,1:04:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,先封锁曼哈顿\N{\fs25}{\i1}to close Manhattan in the first place,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.62,1:04:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我们也不可能在莫斯托的埋伏中\N{\fs25}{\i1}we wouldn't have already neutralized two of the three men responsible{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.35,1:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,干掉那三个人中的两个\N{\fs25}{\i1}for the ambush at Mosto's{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.29,1:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们昨晚害我们第85区分局的\N{\fs25}{\i1}that claimed the lives of eight of our finest{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.59,1:04:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,八名优秀警员殉职\N{\fs25}{\i1}from the 85th Precinct last night.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.75,1:04:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一名枪手已确认是雷蒙德·杰克逊\N{\fs25}{\i1}A gunman identified as Raymond Jackson{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.59,1:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他的同伙 托里亚诺·布什\N{\fs25}{\i1}and his accomplice, Toriano Bush,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.09,1:04:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,两人都于今天凌晨在拒捕中被击毙\N{\fs25}{\i1}both died resisting arrest in the early hours of this morning.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.15,1:04:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,两个人都有武器 很危险\N{\fs25}{\i1}Both men were armed and dangerous.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.75,1:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们英勇的警员在第85分局...\N{\fs25}{\i1}Our brave officers at the 85th Precinct...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.79,1:04:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,85\N{\fs25}Eighty-fifth.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.92,1:04:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,“8-5”\N{\fs25}"Eight-five."
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.42,1:05:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们相信还有第三个同伙\N{\fs25}{\i1}We believe we have the third man,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.35,1:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔·特鲁希略 他已插翅难逃\N{\fs25}{\i1}Michael Trujillo, within our grasp.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.62,1:05:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,85\N{\fs25}Eighty-five.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.96,1:05:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要求所有居民就地避难\N{\fs25}{\i1}We ask all residents to shelter in place{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.96,1:05:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会逮捕特鲁希略 让他为自己的罪行负责\N{\fs25}{\i1}while we apprehend Trujillo and hold him accountable for his crimes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.29,1:05:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,警察编号\N{\fs25}Badge numbers.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.32,1:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,每个编号代表一个警察\N{\fs25}Every number's a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.39,1:05:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,救命！ 救命！救命！\N{\fs25}Help! Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.49,1:05:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我找安保部总监 他在吗?\N{\fs25}Could I speak to the director of security, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.02,1:06:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 先生 稍等\N{\fs25}I'm sorry, Officer, just one moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.82,1:06:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,前台\N{\fs25}Reception.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.26,1:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.56,1:06:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 你不能来这儿\N{\fs25}Sir, you can't be back here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.59,1:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去哪里？\N{\fs25}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.86,1:06:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得活捉他\N{\fs25}We gotta bring him in alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.76,1:06:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在视觉酒店发生了一场袭击 听起来是特鲁希略做的\N{\fs25}{\i1}...assault at the Parallax Hotel. Sounds like Trujillo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.79,1:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,从后方的厨房逃逸\N{\fs25}{\i1}Direction of flight was through the kitchen at rear.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.76,1:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那里是第十三大道 把他堵在那里\N{\fs25}That's 13th Street. Lock him in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.79,1:06:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不准其他人靠近 我来追\N{\fs25}Nobody approach him! He's mine!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.12,1:06:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 站住\N{\fs25}Sir, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.46,1:06:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,站住别动 举起双手\N{\fs25}Hold it right there! Show me your hands!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.46,1:06:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,快开车 从另一头截住他\N{\fs25}Take the car! Cut him off on the other side!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.76,1:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开枪!\N{\fs25}Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.29,1:09:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,特鲁希略 放下武器\N{\fs25}Trujillo! Drop your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.06,1:09:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是警察 停下 趴下\N{\fs25}{\i1}Police. Stop, drop on the ground.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.83,1:09:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开枪! 不要开枪!\N{\fs25}Don't shoot! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.40,1:11:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是警察\N{\fs25}Police.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.83,1:11:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是警察 别动 别动 别动\N{\fs25}Police, don't move, don't move, don't move.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.56,1:11:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,把门口让开 把门口让开\N{\fs25}Clear the doorway. Clear the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.10,1:11:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,别挡着门\N{\fs25}Clear the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.16,1:11:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约警局现在负责查案\N{\fs25}NYPD. Take cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.50,1:11:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让开! 让开!\N{\fs25}Clear! Clear!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.16,1:11:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧让开!\N{\fs25}Come on, clear!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.63,1:11:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,警察 让开 让开\N{\fs25}Police. Clear, clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.36,1:11:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别挡道 纽约警察办案\N{\fs25}Out of the way. NYPD. Take cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.76,1:11:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,快走 快走 快走\N{\fs25}Move. Move. Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.43,1:11:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快离开 快离开 快离开\N{\fs25}Clear. Clear. Clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.50,1:11:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,放下武器\N{\fs25}Drop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.46,1:12:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是今天晚上第一个先讲话后开枪的警察\N{\fs25}You're the only cop tonight who speaks first and shoots second.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.60,1:12:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在已经是早上了 你杀了我们八个人\N{\fs25}It's fucking morning, and you killed eight of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.16,1:12:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不全是好警察\N{\fs25}Not all eight were clean.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.93,1:12:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谁关心这个?\N{\fs25}Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.60,1:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你会\N{\fs25}You do.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.77,1:12:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我跟别人不同?\N{\fs25}How do you know I'm any different?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.23,1:12:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你到现在都没有向我开枪\N{\fs25}Because you would have shot me by now.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.00,1:12:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,之前说的驱动器在哪儿\N{\fs25}Where are those drives we were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.10,1:12:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我藏起来了\N{\fs25}I stashed them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.60,1:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.23,1:12:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我 我会保你活着\N{\fs25}Give them to me, and I'll keep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.50,1:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.83,1:12:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要驱动器 那就放我走\N{\fs25}You want the drives, you let me go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.80,1:12:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不和我一起走出去 你会被其他警察抓的\N{\fs25}If you don't walk out with me, you'll be carried out by others.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.77,1:12:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔 你唯一的希望就是讲出真相\N{\fs25}Michael, your only hope is to tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.93,1:12:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,向上帝请求原谅\N{\fs25}pray to God for forgiveness,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.80,1:12:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要接受的事实是你可能会死在监狱里\N{\fs25}and make peace with the fact that you may die in prison.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.00,1:12:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,现在朝你开枪会是一个更好的选择\N{\fs25}Shooting you sounds a whole lot better right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.70,1:13:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会想我的脸和这个脏乱地铁\N{\fs25}You don't want my face and this dirty subway
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.87,1:13:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是你最后看到的东西\N{\fs25}to be the last things you ever see.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.67,1:13:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我死了 你永远也不会知道驱动器上的内容是什么\N{\fs25}If I die, you'll never find out what's on those drives.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.67,1:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我也许找不到驱动器\N{\fs25}I may not find the drives,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.50,1:13:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我会找出今晚这些事情发生的原因\N{\fs25}but I will find out why tonight happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.67,1:13:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你要怎么证明它?\N{\fs25}But could you prove it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.77,1:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我只需要向我自己证明就行了\N{\fs25}I only have to prove it to myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.57,1:13:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,放下吧 迈克尔\N{\fs25}Come on, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.37,1:13:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,放下吧\N{\fs25}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.80,1:13:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来\N{\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.30,1:13:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,来\N{\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.00,1:13:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,给我\N{\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.30,1:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开枪!\N{\fs25}Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.97,1:14:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开枪!\N{\fs25}Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.17,1:14:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开枪!\N{\fs25}Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.10,1:14:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼\N{\fs25}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.50,1:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞什么鬼\N{\fs25}What the fuck, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.80,1:14:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他在投降 他已经放弃抵抗了\N{\fs25}He was surrendering. He was giving himself up.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.13,1:14:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他要朝你开枪\N{\fs25}He was gonna shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.60,1:14:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你没看到枪已经放下了吗?\N{\fs25}You didn't see the gun down?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.00,1:14:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的 你没看到吗?\N{\fs25}You didn't fucking see the gun down?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.77,1:14:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为他要开枪的\N{\fs25}I thought he was gonna shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.44,1:14:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,控制中心 这里是案发现场 4-3警员 收到请回答\N{\fs25}Central, this is homicide 4-3. Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.87,1:14:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,控制中心 收到请回答\N{\fs25}Central, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.47,1:14:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,请注意 我们在第六节车厢发生交火\N{\fs25}Be advised, we have shots fired on the 6 train
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.20,1:14:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,请赶紧到中央车站\N{\fs25}coming into Grand Central.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.77,1:15:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嫌疑人已被击毙 嫌疑人已被击毙\N{\fs25}Suspect is down. Suspect is down.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.64,1:15:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,密码"Coolhand"\N{\fs25}"Coolhand."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.50,1:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,收到请回答\N{\fs25}Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.64,1:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,控制中心?\N{\fs25}Central?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.40,1:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Coolhand"\N{\fs25}"Coolhand."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.60,1:15:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,控制中心 收到请回答\N{\fs25}Central, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.34,1:15:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,控制中心?\N{\fs25}Central?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.30,1:15:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,控制中心 收到信息请回复\N{\fs25}Central, advise if you receive my transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.84,1:15:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,靠\N{\fs25}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.61,1:16:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了吗？\N{\fs25}Is he gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.47,1:16:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢?\N{\fs25}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.17,1:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这案子他们没找错人\N{\fs25}I think they called the right man for the job.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.61,1:16:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你做得很好\N{\fs25}Hey. Good job. You did great work.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.34,1:16:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就该这么做 做得好\N{\fs25}Way to go. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.27,1:16:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,祝贺你 警探\N{\fs25}Congratulations, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.00,1:16:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 长官\N{\fs25}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.61,1:16:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-了不起  -谢谢你们\N{\fs25}- Amazing. - Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.31,1:17:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs25}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.51,1:17:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs25}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.94,1:17:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-我手机没电了  -哦\N{\fs25}- This fucking thing is dead. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.64,1:17:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可以借一下你的吗?\N{\fs25}Can I borrow yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.17,1:17:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好 当然\N{\fs25}Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.54,1:17:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-我一会儿就还你  -好的\N{\fs25}- I'll bring it right back. - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.97,1:17:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好 警探\N{\fs25}Good work, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.27,1:17:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒 伯恩斯\N{\fs25}Great job, Burns.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.11,1:17:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 凯利\N{\fs25}Thanks, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.74,1:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-手怎么样  -还行\N{\fs25}- How's the hand? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.11,1:17:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 女士\N{\fs25}Okay. Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.51,1:17:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是语音信箱\N{\fs25}Voice mail.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.11,1:17:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,靠\N{\fs25}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.54,1:17:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚真是漫长 你需要好好休息\N{\fs25}It's been a long night. You get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.64,1:18:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 你也是\N{\fs25}Yeah, you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.44,1:18:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快回家抱抱女儿\N{\fs25}Go hug that daughter of yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.44,1:18:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,曼哈顿于今早七点零五分重新开放\N{\fs25}{\i1}Manhattan reopened at 7:05 this morning{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.51,1:18:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在昨晚八名警察遇害之后\N{\fs25}{\i1}after a night of carnage that saw eight police officers...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.14,1:18:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,曼哈顿被封锁 禁止出入\N{\fs25}{\i1}...into and out of Manhattan were closed last night.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.04,1:19:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,亲眼看到了这场成功的追捕\N{\fs25}{\i1}...personally oversee the successful conclusion of the manhunt...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.54,1:19:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约警察成功击毙嫌疑人\N{\fs25}{\i1}...flooded by the NYPD{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.11,1:19:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这看起来像是一场武装袭击\N{\fs25}{\i1}in what looked and felt like a military invasion.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.98,1:19:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?\N{\fs25}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.11,1:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\fs25}Goddammit.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.14,1:19:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 冷静\N{\fs25}Okay, all right, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.48,1:19:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,到我这里来吧\N{\fs25}Just come over to my place.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.31,1:19:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.84,1:19:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\fs25}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.24,1:19:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会尽快解决的\N{\fs25}We'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.34,1:19:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别急\N{\fs25}Just...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.78,1:19:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我先挂电话了\N{\fs25}I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.58,1:19:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我有客人\N{\fs25}I got a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.41,1:19:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的枪放下\N{\fs25}Put your gun down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.61,1:20:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你在跟谁通电话?\N{\fs25}Who was on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.34,1:20:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我老婆\N{\fs25}My wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.38,1:20:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个护士\N{\fs25}She's a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.48,1:20:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,刚准备轮班\N{\fs25}Shift just started.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.64,1:20:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是结婚后的生活\N{\fs25}And that's the story of all married life.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.94,1:20:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你和莫斯托的老板是一伙的\N{\fs25}Guy that owned Mosto's was your partner.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.28,1:20:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,莫斯托是你的金库\N{\fs25}Mosto's was your vault.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.78,1:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,8-5警队是装甲安保部队 你们用警车在城里运送毒品\N{\fs25}The 8-5 was armored security, moving drugs around the city in NYPD vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.81,1:20:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚真是穿道袍都撞鬼\N{\fs25}Last night was just fucking bad luck on every level.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.48,1:20:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的人去莫斯托搬运可卡因时 碰巧遇上去抢货的竞争者\N{\fs25}A rival hits Mosto's at the same time your boys drop by to move a load of coke,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.45,1:20:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,恰好他们训练有素 你的人敌不过阵亡了\N{\fs25}run into men with training, die, badly.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.74,1:21:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那群训练有素的人逃走后 卖掉毒品去洗钱\N{\fs25}Those men with training escape, sell the drugs and clean the money,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.68,1:21:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,又碰巧跟你找的是同一家洗衣店\N{\fs25}coincidentally with the same launderer you use.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.18,1:21:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀人灭口 试图掩盖一切\N{\fs25}And you scorch earth trying to cover it all up.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.45,1:21:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你很厉害\N{\fs25}You're really good.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.81,1:21:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够\N{\fs25}Not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.18,1:21:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚被杀的警察中有几个并没参与\N{\fs25}Not all the cops killed last night were a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.91,1:21:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不管好与坏 他们昨天都是被你害死的\N{\fs25}Clean or dirty, they're all dead 'cause of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.51,1:21:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你应该知道\N{\fs25}So you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.35,1:21:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这并不是为了凯迪拉克和劳力士这些物质财富\N{\fs25}this is not about Cadillacs and fucking Rolexes, material bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.08,1:21:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是 我那些兄弟也不是\N{\fs25}Not for me. Not for most of my guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.31,1:21:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,都是为了生活\N{\fs25}It's about having a life.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.81,1:21:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我管理8-5警队的第一个月 我就参加了两个兄弟的葬礼\N{\fs25}My first month running the 8-5, I went to two of my cops' funerals.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.28,1:22:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,第一个以60英里的时速撞向了桥墩\N{\fs25}First one went 60 miles an hour into a bridge abutment.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.18,1:22:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,当时他体内酒精浓度为0.25\N{\fs25}His blood alcohol was .25.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.28,1:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,第二人也是喝酒喝死的\N{\fs25}Second guy drank himself to death too.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.35,1:22:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,肝硬化\N{\fs25}Cirrhosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.15,1:22:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我有三个手下自己的房子被查封了\N{\fs25}Three of my cops had their homes foreclosed on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.48,1:22:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人也失去了公寓住所\N{\fs25}Another guy lost his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.88,1:22:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为可恶的房东将房租涨了一倍\N{\fs25}Shitty landlord doubled the rent.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.31,1:22:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,8-5警队的离婚率超过百分之七十\N{\fs25}The divorce rate in the 8-5 was over 70%.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.71,1:22:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切是为了让我的警员能留住婚姻\N{\fs25}This is about my cops staying married,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.85,1:22:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,抚养孩子\N{\fs25}raising their kids,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.65,1:22:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,无需每天花四小时堵在路上\N{\fs25}not having to spend four hours a day sitting in traffic,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.61,1:22:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在一个消费不起的城市里摸爬滚打\N{\fs25}crawling to and from a city they can't afford to live in,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.08,1:22:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这个城市一点都不欢迎他们\N{\fs25}a city that actively fucking dislikes them.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.75,1:22:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们仍日日夜夜\N{\fs25}But a city that they protect...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.98,1:22:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用生命守护着这座城市\N{\fs25}with their lives every fucking day.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.95,1:22:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就是如此\N{\fs25}That's what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.85,1:23:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你讲 说金钱买不到幸福的人都是放狗屁\N{\fs25}I'll tell you what, anybody tells you money can't buy happiness is full of shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.68,1:23:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,8-5警队就是证明\N{\fs25}And the 8-5 is proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.45,1:23:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰基·伯恩斯就是证明\N{\fs25}Frankie Burns is proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.98,1:23:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你把她安插进来就是为了监视我吗\N{\fs25}Did you put her on this just to make sure I did your bidding?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.21,1:23:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我安插她是因为她和你一样优秀\N{\fs25}I put her on this 'cause she might be as good as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.05,1:23:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她也失去了一切\N{\fs25}And she's got everything to lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.05,1:23:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,三个人谋杀了我的父亲\N{\fs25}Three guys murdered my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.98,1:23:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他干掉了两人\N{\fs25}He took two with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.28,1:23:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是第三人\N{\fs25}But the third,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.78,1:23:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他把我父亲打的面目全非 血肉模糊\N{\fs25}he hit my dad so many times he broke every bone in his face.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.02,1:23:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们不得不把棺材盖得死死的\N{\fs25}That's why we had to have a closed casket.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.75,1:24:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人告诉法官\N{\fs25}Guy told the judge...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.42,1:24:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至不记得做过这些\N{\fs25}he didn't even remember doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.45,1:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可卡因和粉的的纯度太高\N{\fs25}He was so jacked, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.62,1:24:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,以致他丧失理智\N{\fs25}so high on cocaine and angel dust.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.38,1:24:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,毒品无时无刻不在\N{\fs25}The drugs have always been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.45,1:24:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,随时随地都有\N{\fs25}And they always will be.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.82,1:24:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,人们也会因此丧命\N{\fs25}And people will always die because of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.12,1:24:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人命 警察不能背负这些人命\N{\fs25}That blood, that blood cannot be on the badge.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.12,1:24:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可你的闪存盘也是来路不明\N{\fs25}You can't prove where those flash drives came from.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.75,1:24:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能挡我财路\N{\fs25}And nobody is gonna take the stand against me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.35,1:24:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你若明知山有虎偏向虎山行 那你只能孤军奋战\N{\fs25}So if you go down this road, Andre, you're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.52,1:24:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你的余生都不能活的安心\N{\fs25}You'll be looking over your shoulder the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.45,1:24:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fs25}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.52,1:25:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你也可以选择视而不见\N{\fs25}Or you could just look the other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.25,1:25:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁愿直视魔鬼\N{\fs25}I'd rather look the devil in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.52,1:26:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我打中你了？\N{\fs25}I get you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.29,1:26:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道还问\N{\fs25}You wouldn't ask if you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.82,1:26:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,伤的很重 是不是\N{\fs25}Hurts like a motherfucker, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.69,1:26:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我死不了\N{\fs25}I'll live.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.35,1:26:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你束手就擒就能活下来\N{\fs25}You can if you give yourself up.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.35,1:26:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你唯一的选择\N{\fs25}It's the only choice available to you right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.45,1:26:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,或许\N{\fs25}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.96,1:28:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱动\N{\fs25}Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.49,1:29:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\fs25}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.19,1:29:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了\N{\fs25}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.82,1:29:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的枪放下\N{\fs25}So put your gun down.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.86,1:29:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要转身面向你 伯恩斯\N{\fs25}I'm gonna turn around and face you, Burns.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.19,1:29:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.66,1:29:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我要转身了\N{\fs25}I'm gonna turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.86,1:29:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,驱动器在我这里\N{\fs25}I have the drives.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.96,1:29:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了备份\N{\fs25}I copied them.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.76,1:29:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,内容已经发出去了\N{\fs25}They're already out in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.19,1:29:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你误入歧途了 伯恩斯\N{\fs25}You're going down, Burns.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.93,1:30:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,8-5警队每一个有污点的警察都步入歧途\N{\fs25}Every dirty cop in the 8-5 is going down.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.16,1:30:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了我 就能继续生活\N{\fs25}You pull that trigger, you get life.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.02,1:30:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以陪你女儿一起成长\N{\fs25}Your daughter doesn't need to grow up without her mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.99,1:30:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,警徽也放下\N{\fs25}Badge too.
